{center}
{subhead}PerfectPaint V2.925{def}
{left}
{pp}
(23/4/03)
{pp}
Version 2.925 of the paint program PerfectPaint by Halvadjian Georges is now available.
In this version the following features were added or changed:
{pp}
Improve PPM and PBM format.{p}
Separate Brush, Picture, palette and anim path for each buffer.{p}
New color correction tool:{p}
"Adjust RGB level", "Auto RGB level" and pixel count.{p}
"Chromatic correction" (usefull for chromatic aberration){p}
"Optimize palette" and the arexx command:{p}
Will remove unused color from the palette to reduce the depth of the picture without lost.{p}
Can also sort the palette with unused color in the end.{p}
Fix somme little bug with CMAP palette, brush album{p}
Keyboard F10: Now remove not only toolbox window but all floating window.{p}
Improve text requester {p}
Number of font in listview are now unlimited.{p}
Improve turboprint communication (correct Inch are send, Menu and color works well){p}
New arexx command: pp_GetDPI{p}
Improve template requester, with preview.{p}
Fix a bug (introduced in the last version) with processing tool{p}
New powerfull processing tool:  MagicSpray, will spray current brush or
several brushes (Magic Album) with variation of size, color, rotation,
shadow ... in real time.   Include some MagicProject. Other MagicProject are available on PerfectPaint's
Page.{p}
Little bug fixed with keyboard shortcut {p}
Brush preview is showed with full transparency (album requester){p}
Improve Undo
{pp}
{link http://gothic.fr.free.fr/amiga/}http://gothic.fr.free.fr/amiga/{end}
{pp}
